snippet.title: Stardew Valley - Mobile Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Pelican Town is opening its doors to Mobile devices! Stardew Valley comes first to iOS on October 24th, with more news on the upcoming Android release soon. Pre-Orders available from October 10th!

For more information and to keep up to date with the latest development news, visit the Stardew Valley website: https://stardewvalley.net/

Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/StardewValley/
Website: https://stardewvalley.net/
ConcernedApe on Twitter: https://twitter.com/concernedape
Chucklefish on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ChucklefishLTD

Created by ConcernedApe, published by Chucklefish. Mobile version developed by The Secret Police.
